	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No it has no side effects. The included MMC5 mapper file doesn't work or is incomplete. There is another one that is complete enough to run Castlevania 3 and is available somewhere. I think Loopy made it, but I'm not certain it may have been someone else. Just try it.

		

		</td>
